<br>

<div id="edition" style="display:none; margin-top: 0px;"></div>

<div id="sub-main" >
	<div id="wiki-content-block">

	
		


<p><strong>Sunlight Spear</strong> is a <a class="wiki_link" href="/Miracles">Miracle</a> in Dark Souls 3. To cast a Miracle you must use a <a class="wiki_link" title="Chime" href="/Sacred+Chimes">Chime</a>, <a class="wiki_link" title="Talisman" href="/Talismans">Talisman</a>, or Special Weapons that can cast <a class="wiki_link" title="Miracles" href="/Miracles">Miracles</a>.</p> 
<div id="infobox" class="infobox"> 
 <div class="table-responsive"> 
  <table class="wiki_table"> 
   <tbody> 
    <tr> 
     <th colspan="2"> <h2>Sunlight Spear</h2> </th> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td style="text-align: center;" colspan="2"><img style="display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" src="/file/Dark-Souls-3/sunlight_spear.png" alt="" width="100"></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><strong>Spell Type</strong></td> 
     <td> <p id="toc1">Miracle</p> </td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><strong><img title="Focus Consumption" src="/file/Dark-Souls-3/icon_fp_cost.png" alt="Focus Consumption" width="24" height="24">Focus Cost</strong></td> 
     <td>48</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><strong><img title="Attunement Slots" src="/file/Dark-Souls-3/icon_attunement.png" alt="Attunement Slots" width="24" height="24">Slots Used</strong></td> 
     <td>1</td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><strong>Requirements</strong></td> 
     <td><span style="font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.428571429;">40 Faith</span></td> 
    </tr> 
    <tr> 
     <td><strong>Type</strong></td> 
     <td>Ranged Attack</td> 
    </tr> 
   </tbody> 
  </table> 
 </div> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<blockquote> 
 <p>Miracle of Gwyn, the First Lord. Hurls a sunlight spear.<br><br>The tales of Gwyn's Archdragon hunts describe the inception of the Age of Fire.</p> 
</blockquote> 
<h3>&nbsp;</h3> 
<h3 id="toc2" class="bonfire"><a name="x-Soul Arrow-Acquired From"></a>Acquired From</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Acquired through <a class="wiki_link" href="/Soul+Transposition">Soul Transposition</a> using <a class="wiki_link" href="/Soul+of+the+Lords">Soul of the Lords</a> and 10000 souls</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3>&nbsp;</h3> 
<h3 id="toc3" class="bonfire"><a name="x-Soul Arrow-Notes"></a>Notes</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Deals (spell buff x 2.6) damage.</li> 
 <li>Creates a second hitbox at melee range that deals an extra 67% damage.</li> 
 <li>Sped up at Regulation 1.08 by about a second at ~50 Virtual Dex.</li> 
 <li>It takes approximately 1.2 seconds to cast at max casting speed.</li> 
 <li>This spell is an effective upgrade of <a class="wiki_link" title="Lightning Spear" href="/Lightning+Spear">Lightning Spear</a> and <a class="wiki_link" title="Great Lightning Spear" href="/Great+Lightning+Spear">Great Lightning Spear</a>, but since it's only obtainable after the final boss it won't be much use in a standard playthrough.</li> 
</ul> 
